\itemize{
\item \code{NI}: exact numerical integration via \code{\link{ptdiff_NI}}.
\item \code{MC}: Monte Carlo simulation via \code{\link{ptdiff_MC}}.
\item \code{MM}: Moment-Matching approximation via
